
I nervously ran my fingers through my grayish hair.
What will she say? How will she react? I thought as I drove down another street. I never meant for things to happen like this...
I glanced down at the sticky note that had the address, 1640 North 2360 East. Looking up at the two story house I turned off the car as I got out. Taking a deep breath I walked up to the door. Knocking I waited for the door to open.
"Dad?" Robin asks as she looks at me in shock.
THE END...
